Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:28.41,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}一直温暖的心浇凉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:36.99,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}无论何时 我总是能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:41.59,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}温柔的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:45.06,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}不断旋转的这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:48.97,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}将转向何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:54.89,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}你注视着的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.81,0:20:02.42,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:10.35,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}我们 毫不停歇地奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:17.09,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}似乎能追上 却又抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.58,0:20:19.42,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}距离若远若近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:29.97,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}安静的 下着雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:37.62,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}有一点 寂寞的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:44.91,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}仿佛要安慰这颗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:52.51,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}不断扩大的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:21:00.41,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}无论何时 我总是注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:05.30,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}可爱的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.66,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}不断旋转的这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.79,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}将前往何方？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:18.66,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}我追求的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:25.89,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}有什么在等着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:33.78,EDch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\alpha&H65&}我们 毫不停歇地奔跑
